metadata.name: Madikken PKQ222
metadata.description:
When the moon is up, beware her eyes. She might take your soul and run.

Madikken is one of my OCs. I held a DTIYS-challenge, where 24 artists from all around the world participated. I ended up giving away prints to 7 of the artists who entered. 

This is one of her alternative poses. Inspired by Theodor Kittelsen's "NÃ¸kken" from 1904. "Madikken PKQ222" is created by Norwegian artist PureKimsanity (me).
